set_group_short

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_group_short -  This sets the short description of a group.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int set_group_short(string name,
string short_desc)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the group
%^BOLD%^short_desc%^RESET%^ - the short of the group

.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 if group doesn't exist

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/group_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This sets the short description of a group.

.EP

